divs: Sighting Detailsi was driving alone i-95 a major road way down here in delaware. when i looked up into the sky i saw a round floating disc shaped object he floated up for about 5 seconds then came back down to below the sky. stayed in place for about 3 mins then zoomed up so fast i couldnt believe what i saw. usuasally i can just just say it was a plane cause of the newcastle airport right around the corner but i know most major airplanes and that wasnt one of them this thing was so fast and it was shining a light. when i looked at it it made me feel empty like i couldnt stop staring at it. eventually when it went back up in the air i never seen it again i only pray that i could see another sighting of these other species
trends: There has been one other sighting in New Castle
There were no other sightings in New Castle on or around August 10th 2007
Summary: Round gray circle in the middle.
